                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2013-11-02</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">很容易读的薄薄的小册子，限于篇幅，不够详细深入，但非常顺畅明晰，也是很不错的读本。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="728135207">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-728135207" class="vote-count">0</span>
